# player.png - Player Sprite Sheet
# Size: 8x16 pixels per frame
# Format: PNG, 4-color Game Boy palette
#
# Frame Layout (8 frames total, horizontal strip):
# Frame 0-1: Idle animation (2 frames)
# Frame 2-5: Run animation (4 frames)
# Frame 6:   Jump pose (1 frame)
# Frame 7:   Fall pose (1 frame)
#
# Expected dimensions: 64x16 pixels (8 frames * 8px wide, 16px tall)
#
# To create this sprite:
# 1. Use a pixel art editor (Aseprite, GraphicsGale, etc.)
# 2. Create an 8x16 character sprite
# 3. Animate idle, run, jump, fall states
# 4. Export as horizontal sprite sheet
# 5. Use Game Boy 4-color palette (white, light green, dark green, black)
